assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: STEICO SE develops, produces, and markets ecological construction products made of renewable raw materials worldwide. The company offers flexible and stable wood fiber insulation panels, and facade insulation materials which are used in the new buildings and renovation works; and sealing products for the building shell. It also provides cavity wall insulation made of wood fibers and cellulose. In addition, the company provides construction products, such as I-joists and laminated veneer lumber products; and fibreboards for pinboards or door fills, as well as other products for industrial applications. Further, it is involved in the timber wholesale business; and provision of seminar services to train craftsmen, architects, and trade representatives, as well as people building their own homes. The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Feldkirchen, Germany. STEICO SE is a subsidiary of Schramek GmbH.
